divs: Sighting DetailsWas taking images of the nebula M78 from my driveway in Mar 2nd After processing the images stacking and calibrating I notice that frame 9 out of 20 there appeared what seemed to be an object that was not in the preceeding or post image 9 It appears to. Electronic shutter was open for 2 minutes. It appears a satellite goes by also to the right of the object. I did not observe the actual object but only the result of the capture later Greg
